ProductTrans.Description: This unbeatable beast is perfect for your Team Escape competition, it has no equal! The Hummer H1 Alpha is the civilian version of a military vehicle known as the M988 Humvee, you got mass, performance and durability all in one car. With its 6.6L (402ci) Turbo Duramax LLY V8 turbo diesel engine and the Allison 1000 5-speed transmission it has an impressive compression ratio of 17.5:1 at 305 bhp @3000 rpm and 605 lbft @1600 rpm there is no stopping this mammoth from taking down anything in its path!
